And I take pleasure
in the senses.

00:47:16.690 --> 00:47:19.220
I stop and smell fresh
cut grass.

00:47:19.220 --> 00:47:21.430
I smell a flower on the way.

00:47:21.430 --> 00:47:25.910
I don't let a second go by.

