in every night.

00:47:35.330 --> 00:47:37.470
And every night, he would
order bourbon.

00:47:37.470 --> 00:47:40.090
And he was a great guy.

00:47:40.090 --> 00:47:45.500
His wife who this guy loved
passionately had passed away

00:47:45.500 --> 00:47:46.320
several years back.

00:47:46.320 --> 00:47:48.010
And he never really
got over it.

00:47:48.010 --> 00:47:49.450
They used to go out dancing
all the time.

00:47:49.450 --> 00:47:50.710
He would love to dance.

00:47:50.710 --> 00:47:52.190
And I would talk to this guy.

00:47:52.190 --> 00:47:53.660
He was a delightful guy.

00:47:53.660 --> 00:47:56.050
But then they would come a point
in the evening were he

00:47:56.050 --> 00:47:58.190
would turn and go
to the jukebox.

00:47:58.190 --> 00:48:02.300
And that was my cue to
give him a space.

00:48:02.300 --> 00:48:05.710
He would play one song, L7.

00:48:05.710 --> 00:48:09.330
And it was "Harvest Moon"
by Neil Young.

00:48:09.330 --> 00:48:12.570
And he would go back, and
he'd sit in his chair.

00:48:12.570 --> 00:48:15.140
And his eyes would close.

00:48:15.140 --> 00:48:18.050
And his head would do this.

00:48:18.050 --> 00:48:23.094
And he physically was there
but wasn't there.

00:48:23.094 --> 00:48:25.780
He was mentally transported.

00:48:25.780 --> 00:48:30.960
And he was dancing with
his wife, I am sure.

00:48:30.960 --> 00:48:33.070
And he was zoned out.

00:48:33.070 --> 00:48:35.190
And it was such an unbelievably
beautiful thing

00:48:35.190 --> 00:48:39.940
to see, to watch him do that,
and to see every single note

00:48:39.940 --> 00:48:40.870
of that song.

00:48:40.870 --> 00:48:44.220
He soaked it in, like
it was gold.

00:48:44.220 --> 00:48:46.950
And he did that every night.

00:48:46.950 --> 00:48:48.730
And it's interesting.

00:48:48.730 --> 00:48:52.890
Poor guy passed away
this year.

00:48:52.890 --> 00:48:55.960
And I actually, evenings
at my lake house,

00:48:55.960 --> 00:48:57.220
I'll play Neil Young.

00:48:57.220 --> 00:48:58.730
And I'll do one of these.

00:48:58.730 --> 00:49:00.730
Because I know he's
the dancing.

